1
00:00:01,510 --> 00:00:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bring you a tip.</font>

2
00:00:05,350 --> 00:00:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The crown prince, Second Prince Albert,</font>

3
00:00:10,410 --> 00:00:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">plans to lead
a coup tonight...</font>

4
00:00:13,230 --> 00:00:15,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and force His Majesty 
to abdicate the throne.</font>

5
00:00:30,590 --> 00:00:32,550
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#817c4f"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="10">Born Blessed, So I'll Obtain Ultimate Power</font></b></font></font></font>

6
00:00:30,590 --> 00:00:32,550
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#051529">m 0 0 l 235 0 l 225 8 l 235 15 l 18 15 l 30 8 l 18 0</font></font>

7
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:50,960
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Episode 12</font></b></font></font>

8
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:50,960
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Nobility</font></b></font></font>

9
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Albert?</i></font>

10
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, wait a minute.</i></font>

11
00:01:57,690 --> 00:01:59,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said your name was Olivia?</font>

12
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know this?</font>

13
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the daughter of Coil, a member of 
former First Prince Gilbert's household.</font>

14
00:02:08,770 --> 00:02:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coil, his butler?</font>

15
00:02:10,650 --> 00:02:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were born into the household?</font>

16
00:02:12,170 --> 00:02:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

17
00:02:13,110 --> 00:02:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Born into a household...</i></font>

18
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:20,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That refers to a child born between 
two servants of a prince's house.</i></font>

19
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since that's the environment 
they grow up in,</i></font>

20
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it's easy for them to swear 
absolute loyalty to that prince.</i></font>

21
00:02:28,990 --> 00:02:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know all about how you managed</font>

22
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to spare the First Prince's life.</font>

23
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet, that man...</font>

24
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see. At the time, my 
father was probably...</i></font>

25
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:48,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I swore revenge and approached him...</font>

26
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with this body my parents gave me.</font>

27
00:02:52,590 --> 00:02:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then I heard it.</font>

28
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before the official proclamation 
of his disinheritance,</font>

29
00:03:00,020 --> 00:03:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while he was still the crown prince,</font>

30
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:07,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he would mobilize soldiers and 
take control of the palace.</font>

31
00:03:11,150 --> 00:03:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does Albert intend 
to do to His Majesty?</font>

32
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Force him to abdicate and become 
an emperor emeritus, he said.</font>

33
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:24,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I beg of you!</font>

34
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My body, my very life...</font>

35
00:03:27,330 --> 00:03:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are yours to use as you see fit!</font>

36
00:03:29,610 --> 00:03:33,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just, please... stop Crown Prince Albert!</font>

37
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please...</font>

38
00:03:36,660 --> 00:03:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

39
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you do at Gilbert's house?</font>

40
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I was an apprentice 
butler under my father.</font>

41
00:03:48,350 --> 00:03:50,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you'll do that here, too.</font>

42
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be paid the same 
as you were there.</font>

43
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From tomorrow on, you don't 
need to do anything special.</font>

44
00:03:57,860 --> 00:04:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why... would you treat me so well?</font>

45
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you lost your master, 
you tried to avenge him.</font>

46
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:08,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I merely acknowledged your loyalty</font>

47
00:04:08,230 --> 00:04:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in serving your master to the 
end, even after his death.</font>

48
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How remarkable you are...</font>

49
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:16,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I humbly offer myself in your service!</font>

50
00:04:20,860 --> 00:04:24,320
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#fefefd">Dark</font></b></font></font></font>

51
00:04:34,690 --> 00:04:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master?</font>

52
00:04:36,740 --> 00:04:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going out for a bit.</font>

53
00:04:38,300 --> 00:04:40,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-All right! Um... A carriage, then?</font>

54
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I'll go alone.</font>

55
00:04:42,490 --> 00:04:43,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

56
00:04:48,210 --> 00:04:50,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But it's so late...</font>

57
00:04:50,940 --> 00:04:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gigi.</font>

58
00:04:58,080 --> 00:05:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We shall await your return, Master.</font>

59
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

60
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please be safe.</font>

61
00:05:15,690 --> 00:05:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If Albert intends to use 
his right of command,</i></font>

62
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>there's only one force he could lead.</i></font>

63
00:05:29,340 --> 00:05:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's stationed at the Ministry 
of Military Affairs.</font>

64
00:05:41,870 --> 00:05:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A thousand men.</font>

65
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since they're permanently stationed,</font>

66
00:05:50,090 --> 00:05:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they've been trained to obey the orders</font>

67
00:05:53,110 --> 00:05:56,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of the superior officer in command 
without a second thought.</font>

68
00:05:58,650 --> 00:05:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hear me!</font>

69
00:05:59,890 --> 00:06:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you familiar with the 
saying, "Even water can rot"?</font>

70
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:09,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Water that forgets to flow and 
stays in one place too long</font>

71
00:06:09,980 --> 00:06:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">eventually stagnates and becomes 
a home for all manner of vermin.</font>

72
00:06:14,900 --> 00:06:17,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same can be said of a nation!</font>

73
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Majesty has forgotten 
to flow for far too long,</font>

74
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now, vermin swarm around him in the 
form of disloyal, treacherous retainers,</font>

75
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">trying to rot this country 
from the inside!</font>

76
00:06:30,860 --> 00:06:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Justice sides with me!</font>

77
00:06:33,170 --> 00:06:38,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will return the empire you love to 
the hands in which it was meant to be!</font>

78
00:06:47,790 --> 00:06:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please hold, Brother!</font>

79
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, Noah. What brings 
you here at this hour?</font>

80
00:06:56,340 --> 00:06:58,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please refrain from doing 
anything senseless!</font>

81
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is still time!</font>

82
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:04,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who told you?</font>

83
00:07:04,150 --> 00:07:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't matter!</font>

84
00:07:06,660 --> 00:07:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother, if you take this step, you 
will bring about your own ruin!</font>

85
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:13,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What of it?!</font>

86
00:07:13,010 --> 00:07:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I refuse to die while sitting 
around doing nothing!</font>

87
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die?</font>

88
00:07:19,020 --> 00:07:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't read His Majesty's edict 
regarding your disinheritance?</font>

89
00:07:24,150 --> 00:07:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know the agony
His Majesty felt writing that?!</font>

90
00:07:29,710 --> 00:07:34,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what you may have done, 
he did not disclose it publicly.</font>

91
00:07:39,150 --> 00:07:42,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Majesty wants you to live!</font>

92
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:45,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He agonized over a way to 
allow you to keep your life!</font>

93
00:07:45,110 --> 00:07:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I should be content with 
just being a prince?!</font>

94
00:07:49,230 --> 00:07:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thirty-five years...</font>

95
00:07:51,450 --> 00:07:53,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I waited thirty-five years!</font>

96
00:07:53,670 --> 00:07:57,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believed that I would sit 
on that throne one day...</font>

97
00:07:57,470 --> 00:08:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that I would rule this empire!</font>

98
00:08:00,980 --> 00:08:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this is what I get?!</font>

99
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:09,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Majesty seems to value his own 
life above all in his old age.</font>

100
00:08:09,650 --> 00:08:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he insists on clinging 
pathetically to the throne,</font>

101
00:08:13,110 --> 00:08:18,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will oust him with military might, 
as is befitting of a military nation.</font>

102
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Content with just being a prince?</i></font>

103
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>From the perspective 
of the common folk,</i></font>

104
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as well as my own,
the status of prince is most noble.</i></font>

105
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They do what they think is best,</i></font>

106
00:08:33,430 --> 00:08:37,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and have the power to act in 
the interests of the people.</i></font>

107
00:08:37,410 --> 00:08:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A prince is born blessed.</i></font>

108
00:08:40,370 --> 00:08:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But since Albert was 
once the crown prince,</i></font>

109
00:08:43,540 --> 00:08:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>being reduced to that status 
must be akin to death.</i></font>

110
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:50,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This vast difference 
in values must mean...</i></font>

111
00:08:52,190 --> 00:08:54,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You insist on trying to stop me?</font>

112
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

113
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

114
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's the kind of 
younger brother you are.</font>

115
00:09:06,610 --> 00:09:08,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apprehend Noah!</font>

116
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a traitor!</font>

117
00:09:12,530 --> 00:09:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A thousand of them.</i></font>

118
00:09:22,970 --> 00:09:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They still follow orders faithfully, even 
if ordered to attack a prince.</i></font>

119
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:29,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They are indeed well-trained.</i></font>

120
00:09:29,690 --> 00:09:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All the more reason I can't 
involve them in this!</i></font>

121
00:09:38,900 --> 00:09:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come!</font>

122
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Master.</i></font>

123
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Summon the power you 
desire by its true name.</i></font>

124
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The power... I desire...</i></font>

125
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go, Luthier!</font>

126
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

127
00:10:02,890 --> 00:10:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bahamut!</font>

128
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Flowing water allows no contamination.</i></font>

129
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A breath of wind becomes the 
eyes and ears that know all.</font>

130
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The earth is the foundation to 
support the feet that move forward.</i></font>

131
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:35,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And flame...</i></font>

132
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>manifests here as the 
power to burn all to ash!</i></font>

133
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:52,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What is that?!</font>

134
00:11:06,420 --> 00:11:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough.</font>

135
00:11:08,270 --> 00:11:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't kill any soldiers.</font>

136
00:11:29,560 --> 00:11:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's over, Brother.</font>

137
00:11:33,090 --> 00:11:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll kill me? You? <i>You</i>?!</font>

138
00:11:37,290 --> 00:11:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I will not take your life.</font>

139
00:11:42,250 --> 00:11:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Majesty would most certainly be sad 
if one of his sons killed another.</font>

140
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

141
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:51,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poison?!</font>

142
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Precisely.</font>

143
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will not kill you myself,</font>

144
00:11:56,740 --> 00:11:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I will not stop you 
from killing yourself.</font>

145
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be serious! Who do you think you are?!</font>

146
00:12:03,970 --> 00:12:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you considered?</font>

147
00:12:06,450 --> 00:12:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I kill you, then you and all 
your family and subordinates</font>

148
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will be executed as traitors.</font>

149
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you kill yourself now,</font>

150
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the story will be that you led 
a force to attempt mutiny,</font>

151
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but stopped at the last moment 
and killed yourself instead.</font>

152
00:12:26,660 --> 00:12:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You cannot erase this act from existence.</font>

153
00:12:30,980 --> 00:12:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you can still spare your 
family and subordinates,</font>

154
00:12:35,030 --> 00:12:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and your eldest son can 
still succeed you...</font>

155
00:12:39,010 --> 00:12:42,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The choice is yours, Brother.</font>

156
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:45,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would fall for such nonsense?!</font>

157
00:12:46,070 --> 00:12:48,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Foster! Howard!</font>

158
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:49,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apprehend this boy!</font>

159
00:12:56,340 --> 00:12:57,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not over yet.</font>

160
00:12:57,910 --> 00:13:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill that dotard and 
take the throne if I must—</font>

161
00:13:05,230 --> 00:13:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you doing?!</font>

162
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can no longer follow you.</font>

163
00:13:10,310 --> 00:13:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even under these 
circumstances, Prince Noah</font>

164
00:13:13,140 --> 00:13:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">showed consideration for your 
family and subordinates.</font>

165
00:13:16,760 --> 00:13:18,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet <i>this</i> is what you're doing?!</font>

166
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you mad?! I'm telling you 
not to entertain his nonsense!</font>

167
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silence!</font>

168
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:25,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you...</font>

169
00:13:26,420 --> 00:13:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember the 120 people 
you sacrificed to the miasma</font>

170
00:13:30,460 --> 00:13:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when you lifted the seal on 
Leviathan all those years ago?!</font>

171
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's what...</i></font>

172
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:46,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My older brother was one of them!</font>

173
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My friend from childhood, too!</font>

174
00:13:48,250 --> 00:13:50,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father was among them, as well.</font>

175
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't follow you any longer!</font>

176
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't expect me to!</font>

177
00:13:54,950 --> 00:13:58,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nonsense! I am the crown prince!</font>

178
00:13:58,540 --> 00:14:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your lives belong to m—</font>

179
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Noah, it seems the
crown prince regrets his actions</font>

180
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:07,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and has chosen to commit suicide.</font>

181
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

182
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:09,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

183
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Olivia.</font>

184
00:14:11,810 --> 00:14:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

185
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

186
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You can't be serious!</font>

187
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you forgotten your debt 
to me for taking you in?!</font>

188
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Stop...</font>

189
00:14:50,290 --> 00:14:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn... you all...</font>

190
00:14:53,090 --> 00:14:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who do you... think I...</font>

191
00:15:05,810 --> 00:15:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thirty-five years...</i></font>

192
00:15:08,010 --> 00:15:10,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I waited thirty-five years.</i></font>

193
00:15:10,610 --> 00:15:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I believed that I would sit 
on that throne one day...</i></font>

194
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that I would rule this empire.</i></font>

195
00:15:27,050 --> 00:15:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother...</font>

196
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Noah.</font>

197
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tragically, Prince Albert, the man 
who led us, has committed suicide.</font>

198
00:15:41,660 --> 00:15:44,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His treacherous ambitions led him 
to take command of our army,</font>

199
00:15:44,980 --> 00:15:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he realized the gravity of his 
crime and deeply regretted it.</font>

200
00:15:49,470 --> 00:15:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In his last moments, he begged that 
his bereaved family be shown mercy.</font>

201
00:15:53,130 --> 00:15:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. My brother attempted a coup,</font>

202
00:15:57,090 --> 00:15:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but due to a tip from a 
loyal household member</font>

203
00:16:00,550 --> 00:16:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the bravery of his retainers in 
risking their lives to stop him,</font>

204
00:16:03,830 --> 00:16:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he got no farther than taking 
command of some soldiers.</font>

205
00:16:06,750 --> 00:16:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Therefore, under imperial law,</font>

206
00:16:09,490 --> 00:16:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the informant and retainers 
will be rewarded,</font>

207
00:16:12,140 --> 00:16:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and other household members 
will be overlooked.</font>

208
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will encourage His Majesty to have 
my brother's eldest son succeed him.</font>

209
00:16:19,890 --> 00:16:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Your Highness.</font>

210
