211
00:16:22,450 --> 00:16:31,920
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#3c4e5e">m 0 0 l 268 0 268 88 0 88</font></font>

212
00:16:23,090 --> 00:16:25,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My basic abilities went way up.</i></font>

213
00:16:25,980 --> 00:16:28,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>These two must be very strong.</i></font>

214
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Albert had subordinates 
this talented turn on him?</i></font>

215
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People really are treasures.</font>

216
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But since he didn't appreciate that,</i></font>

217
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>his coup was doomed to fail either way.</i></font>

218
00:16:52,980 --> 00:16:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is where you've been.</font>

219
00:16:58,230 --> 00:17:02,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a moment ago, this box reacted.</font>

220
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps Noah's magic sword 
has begun to awaken.</font>

221
00:17:07,410 --> 00:17:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given Prince Noah's talent, 
I can believe it.</font>

222
00:17:16,060 --> 00:17:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... what happened?</font>

223
00:17:19,180 --> 00:17:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After receiving word around the same 
time we did, Noah rushed to the scene.</font>

224
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the crown prince...</font>

225
00:17:28,220 --> 00:17:33,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">took his own life with poison.</font>

226
00:17:34,050 --> 00:17:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

227
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave me alone for a while.</font>

228
00:17:50,300 --> 00:17:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah, even at a time like 
this, you are remarkable.</font>

229
00:17:57,450 --> 00:17:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so...</i></font>

230
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:01,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gilbert Ararat</i></font>

231
00:18:02,970 --> 00:18:04,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and Albert Ararat,</i></font>

232
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the two princes who attempted to murder 
the emperor and take his throne,</i></font>

233
00:18:09,990 --> 00:18:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>disappeared from this world.</i></font>

234
00:18:14,210 --> 00:18:15,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a result,</font>

235
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:22,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Meeres Empire saw the beginning of a 
new era of peace like none before.</font>

236
00:18:24,930 --> 00:18:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! That's amazing!</font>

237
00:18:28,210 --> 00:18:32,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that prince was around the 
same age as you, right, Sister?</font>

238
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:35,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet he... That's amazing!</font>

239
00:18:36,520 --> 00:18:39,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then? What happened next?</font>

240
00:18:42,870 --> 00:18:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know not.</font>

241
00:18:44,650 --> 00:18:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

242
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because this story...</font>

243
00:18:51,060 --> 00:18:54,980
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="15"><font color="#dde5e7">Three Years Later</font></font></font></b></font>

244
00:18:56,610 --> 00:19:00,610
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="15"><font color="#dde5e7">Nishil, Capital of Almeria</font></font></font></b></font>

245
00:19:05,040 --> 00:19:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at this, Head Maid!</font>

246
00:19:08,790 --> 00:19:11,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's from Evelyn!</font>

247
00:19:11,370 --> 00:19:13,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, so it is.</font>

248
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's take our time reading it later.</font>

249
00:19:15,450 --> 00:19:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll never finish if we 
don't work efficiently.</font>

250
00:19:17,010 --> 00:19:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Prince Noah is amazing.</font>

251
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still more?!</font>

252
00:19:19,050 --> 00:19:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}He's more popular than ever.</font>

253
00:19:20,630 --> 00:19:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Still, this is way too much!</font>

254
00:19:20,930 --> 00:19:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're for both his fifteenth birthday</font>

255
00:19:22,490 --> 00:19:23,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Right?</font>

256
00:19:25,410 --> 00:19:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and his relocation to Almeria 
to officially rule as its lord.</font>

257
00:19:28,950 --> 00:19:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are still two more rooms' worth.</font>

258
00:19:30,960 --> 00:19:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? He gets more 
and more every year...</font>

259
00:19:34,520 --> 00:19:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, he's Prince Noah, after all.</font>

260
00:19:37,730 --> 00:19:42,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That just shows how many 
people he has saved,</font>

261
00:19:45,190 --> 00:19:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and how many people want 
to be of use to him.</font>

262
00:19:52,670 --> 00:19:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our master is amazing, isn't he?</font>

263
00:19:55,080 --> 00:19:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, he truly is.</font>

264
00:19:58,470 --> 00:20:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if you would finish up here.</font>

265
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure!</font>

266
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your skill is as impressive as ever.</font>

267
00:20:17,490 --> 00:20:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Audrey.</font>

268
00:20:19,050 --> 00:20:21,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would you like to do for breakfast?</font>

269
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have it here.</font>

270
00:20:23,010 --> 00:20:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

271
00:20:24,860 --> 00:20:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zoey.</font>

272
00:20:26,020 --> 00:20:27,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

273
00:20:35,750 --> 00:20:36,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you are.</font>

274
00:20:36,820 --> 00:20:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

275
00:20:38,470 --> 00:20:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just about time.</font>

276
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:41,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

277
00:20:41,810 --> 00:20:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My fifteenth birthday, when 
I am stripped of my surname.</font>

278
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How I have long waited for the day!</font>

279
00:20:48,150 --> 00:20:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you'll be losing your surname.</font>

280
00:20:51,040 --> 00:20:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes me happy.</font>

281
00:20:53,090 --> 00:20:59,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because this means I finally, 
officially become your wife!</font>

282
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be so impatient.</font>

283
00:21:01,250 --> 00:21:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, I have no intention</font>

284
00:21:05,840 --> 00:21:09,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of giving the one I have welcomed 
over my threshold to anyone else.</font>

285
00:21:09,100 --> 00:21:10,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

286
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was talking to the emperor,</font>

287
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it sounds like one of those 
three will be next in line.</font>

288
00:21:19,210 --> 00:21:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fourth prince, Henry...</font>

289
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The eighth prince, Oscar...</font>

290
00:21:31,730 --> 00:21:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the one he's hoping 
for is... that one.</font>

291
00:21:35,710 --> 00:21:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care.</font>

292
00:21:37,730 --> 00:21:38,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care.</font>

293
00:21:39,190 --> 00:21:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care.</font>

294
00:21:40,730 --> 00:21:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care.</font>

295
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care.</font>

296
00:21:54,750 --> 00:21:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'll go ahead and 
bet it all on that boy.</font>

297
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care, Prince Noah.</font>

298
00:22:04,550 --> 00:22:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

299
